---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="content-shell py-12 md:py-16 space-y-10 max-w-2xl">

    <header class="space-y-4 border-b border-[color:var(--color-border)] pb-8">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Almost a Footnote</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Technically a law student. Practically, someone who reads too many judgments and has opinions about all of them.
      </p>
      <p>
        This blog is not a portfolio. It is not a personal brand exercise. It is a place to think out loud about law — the way it reasons, the way it fails to reason, and the gap between what a statute says and what it ends up meaning in practice.
      </p>
      <p>
        The focus is corporate law, arbitration, and intellectual property. The method is close reading. The posts are the point.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you want the CV, you probably already have it. If you want to know how I think, start reading.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3 border-t border-[color:var(--color-border)] pt-8">
      <a href="/blog" class="underline underline-offset-4 text-sm">
        View all writing
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>
</BaseLayout>
